ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2007-2008
PrecisAppointment of SCOTT FRASER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Finland; PIERRE GUIMOND as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Hungary, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Slovenia; ALAIN LATULIPPE as Ambassador of Canada to the Eastern Republic of Uruguay; THOMAS MacDONALD as Consul General of Canada in Sydney (Commonwealth of Australia); ROBERT McRAE as Ambassador and Permanent Representative of Canada to the North Atlantic Council (NATO), in Brussels; DARREN SCHEMMER as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Ghana, with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador to the Togolese Republic; and MARGARET HUBER as Ambassador of Canada to the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan.
